description.title: Letterboxd 500 most watched movies of all time
subtitle: Updated as of: March 30th, 2025
Hope you all enjoy and let me know if a movie is missing :)
Percentage watched by me: 55%.
* Barbie is #1 with 5,16M views
* Ford v Ferrari is #500 with 1M views
Monthly changes:
* Dirty Dancing (#499) and The Lego Batman Movie (#500) are new on this list. Kingsman: The Golden Circle and We're the Millers are out
* Anora (+109), Nosferatu (+33), The Substance (+29), Wicked (+26), Gladiator II (+23), How to Lose a Guy in 10 Days (+21) and Longlegs (+16) gained the most spots
* Room (-13), Gravity (-10), Booksmart (-9), Kick-Ass (-9) and The French Dispatch (-9) lost the most spots
Movies that are close to an entrance:
* Hotel Transylvania (998K views)
* mother! (997K views)
* Carrie (997K views)
* Kingsman: The Golden Circle (994K views)
* We're the Millers (991K views)
Trending movies that will sooner or later be in this list:
